PART A: Fine Zoom k in [3.150, 3.200], step 0.001

Geometric prediction for explosion threshold:
  beta = 299 + k*pi/10. As beta -> 300, 300 - beta -> 0.
  ||p*beta|| ~ (300 - beta)*p  (mod 1, small quantity)
  Criterion ||p*beta|| < 1/p becomes: (300-beta)*p < 1/p
  i.e., p < 1/sqrt(300-beta) = p_thresh
  All primes below p_thresh are swept into S_beta.

